Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Refurbished space - Exposure your business here!

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located on busy Blues Point Road, metres from the corner of Union Street and the renowned Commodore Hotel, this prime retail shop is currently the only retail vacancy on the strip. Available now just in time for Christmas trade, this strip mall location is walking distance to North Sydney CBD and services both residents of the area and commercial office users.

- 68.5sqm*
- Excellent exposure with floor to ceiling glass frontage
- Easy to configure floor plate with rear access to amenities
- Parking on site available if required
- Ducted air conditioning
- Signage opportunities including light box
- Timed street parking directly in front of premises
- Located at the base of an 8 storey commercial building other tenants including Anytime Fitness, Chedi Thai and McMahons Point Grocer
- Neighbouring retailers on the strip include Toni & Guy, Blues Point Pharmacy, Stone Real Estate, Chambers Cellars, Australia Post plus an abundance of cafes and eateries
- Would suit general retail, beauty, fashion, medical, services or possible food use (STCA)

For further details or to arrange an inspection, please contact Amy Pfeiffer 0401 198 401, amy.pfeiffer@cbre.com.au.

*Approx.
